The development of clean technologies from production processes to deep conversion and transportation methods.  4. Creation of an ecosystem for searching and funding developments and of process facilities for the implementation of the developments.

Title: [ANN]ğŸ”¥RUSGASğŸ”¥: a blockchain for a technological breakthrough in the gas industry
Body: https://i.imgur.com/MP3YPuS.jpg?1   Our goal is to unite researchers and gas companies to create an ecosystem that will bring gas technologies up to a qualitatively new level. To improve the environment, to optimise the consumption of natural resources, and to reduce the production costs of valuable compounds.   https://i.imgur.com/MI1ceoy.jpg?2 https://i.imgur.com/MUffLXW.jpg   The gas sector and blockchain technologies have a high potential for mutual adaptation. The huge capacity of the gas market itself comblned with underfunding of innovative approaches calls for investing a new type of money and a new type of contractual relations in this very field.   https://i.imgur.com/5LCLPge.png?1 https://i.imgur.com/jOqreHk.jpg   RusGas is a promising technological project that opens the possibllity for everyone to make contribution to the scientific progress in one of the most important and profitable spheres in the 21st century. And also to take part in improving the environmental situation and preserving the planet's species diversity.   https://i.imgur.com/eDuo08Y.jpg https://i.imgur.com/4C5GJ4v.jpg https://i.imgur.com/XRRpspL.jpg https://i.imgur.com/3CrBG31.jpg   Why have we decided to launch the ICO campaign for RusGas? lt provides a number of advantages for both our project and for holders of our tokens including:  The possibllity of acquiring by any person in any part of the world Security of money transfers and guaranteed receipt of the money High profit margins supported not only by success of a company but also by the interest in it in the market The opportunity for further use of this technology in the company's developments by integrating it into the gas sector and creating IT products thus transforming the industry The opportunity to reward investors and fans with additional bonuses The opportunity to grow beyond the gas industry and to create an ecosystem for research projects in any field   https://i.imgur.com/gBdw5ta.jpg?1   You will be able to purchase RGS tokens during the Token Sale by making a direct ETH transfer to the address of a smart contract. We accept ETH only from cryptocurrency wallets. Be careful and remember that you should not make payments from wallets that are incompatible with the ERC20 contracts or from the cryptocurrency exchange account because it can result in loss of control over the tokens you have acquired.    https://i.imgur.com/kQrfBir.jpg?1 https://i.imgur.com/tHikqLs.jpg?1 https://i.imgur.com/k85r07E.jpg https://i.imgur.com/jxmfH38.jpg https://i.imgur.com/TQW6B8Y.jpg
